General:

Structure:
    Aim to be at least thread-safe and ideally thread-hot.
    Add MEMCACHED_BEHAVIOR_USER_DATA structure
        hold last memcached_return value
        will also hold PrintError & RaiseError flags
    Add memcached_perl_err($memc) to return last memcached_return value

Errors:
    Is success true or false?
    Make return type a dual-var like $! with integer and string message parts.
        add tests for it

